Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:39.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:43.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我櫻田茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為這次選舉的候選人…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.80,0:02:46.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已經在了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.29,0:02:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快點把攝像機架好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:50.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連電視台都來了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是機會啊  茜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.18,0:02:53.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣大家都能聽到你的宣言了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.45,0:02:55.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:59.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先第一個候選公約是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.69,0:03:03.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將監視攝像頭廢除…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:07.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給大家一個平靜安穩的日常生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.90,0:03:11.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別那樣盯著我看…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.76,0:03:14.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.08,0:03:19.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在此向大家保證…
