Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:54.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守護人們安全的假面英雄玫瑰颱風XX
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.31,0:03:59.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  其真實身份是班上第一冒失鬼花江的事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.87,0:04:00.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.29,0:04:02.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早就暴露了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:04.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就騙騙小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.62,0:04:07.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暴露的話花江會變成兔子的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,節目也會完結的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.77,0:04:13.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是知道了她的真實身份  大家都會感謝花江的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:15.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.78,0:04:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓茜做蒙面英雄？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.33,0:04:22.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  將身份隱藏起來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜也就能積極地去幫助別人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後在選舉前將她的身份暴露的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.79,0:04:30.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該能使她的人氣急劇上升
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.16,0:04:31.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:32.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.55,0:04:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陪著茜進行演說我意識到了一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.50,0:04:37.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不是王族
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:39.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她繼續以那種性格的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.56,0:04:42.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我擔心將來她面對很多事時會很艱難
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.31,0:04:47.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我也明白茜正以自己的方式拚命想改變自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.65,0:04:51.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過要是能讓她有大方站在別人面前的實際經驗的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.96,0:04:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想可以慢慢增加她的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.02,0:04:55.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微等等
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.84,0:04:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.43,0:05:10.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:12.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.36,0:05:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼鏡？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:15.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干擾眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.08,0:05:19.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是一旦戴上就能讓周圍的人無法辨認的眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.74,0:05:22.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做蒙面英雄的時候  把這個作為變身道具使用吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.31,0:05:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奏  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是特意去生成出來的吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.52,0:05:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.41,0:05:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然我覺得她只是從自己的房間裏拿了副眼鏡過來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不相信我的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:35.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  謝謝  奏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:40.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過  我為了削減生成的成本
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:43.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓效果只會在茜戴上時發動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.71,0:05:46.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  對於知道這副眼鏡性能的人來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,效果會很薄弱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.38,0:05:53.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  不必勉強使用
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.83,0:05:56.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  會很小心地使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.45,0:05:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:00.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.77,0:06:02.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是和平時的感覺不同了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:04.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.44,0:06:06.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個孩子是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.34,0:06:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還能是誰  茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:12.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂的吧  修
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不認識的女孩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.37,0:06:16.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了  沒有暴露
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.03,0:06:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你剛剛說了「啊」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.62,0:06:19.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這些
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:21.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是相當可愛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(800,0)\fs60\fscx85\fsp7.5\3c&H041515&\bord3\pos(1404,133.5)}茜FANCLUB
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.97,0:06:23.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打擾你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.52,0:06:26.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個人是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.64,0:06:29.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.79,0:06:31.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不認識的人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.21,0:06:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不認識的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.04,0:06:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是為了正義所撒的謊吧  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戴著眼鏡的茜過來的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:42.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要騙她說是不認識的人哦  知道了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:45.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了茜姐姐的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時也是需要善意的謊言的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:50.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:52.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刊哭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.38,0:06:56.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是因為有不認識的女人在家裏感到害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.31,0:06:58.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,刊  是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是茜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.29,0:07:04.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起  嚇到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:06.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是嚇了一跳啊  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.50,0:07:10.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒙面英雄計劃  正式開始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.37,0:07:13.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜託了  去救救它
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.15,0:07:16.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它沒法下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.78,0:07:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真頭疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.91,0:07:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個高度的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:20.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:23.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:28.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs63}好帥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:27.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:28.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.90,0:07:32.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  不能這麼亂來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.78,0:07:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你  大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.86,0:07:39.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…莫非你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.78,0:07:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,櫻田同學…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.20,0:07:43.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:45.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「我是」？
